Class BoardPartitionSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • BoardPartitionSetup
  • public class BoardPartitionSetup
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to store information about how a board partitions shape and what squares are burnt / contain pieces. This was used throughout development for testing how different partitions are favourable, via simulation tests.
